# File Naming Conventions

## Mobile (`mobile/`)

### Components — PascalCase

All component files (`*.tsx`) inside `src/components/` use **PascalCase**, matching the exported component name.

```
src/components/ui/Button.tsx          → export const Button
src/components/ui/SearchBar.tsx       → export const SearchBar
src/components/setup/AccountTypePickerModal.tsx → export const AccountTypePickerModal
```

### Hooks & Stores — camelCase with `use` prefix

```
src/hooks/useAuthListener.ts
src/stores/useSetupStore.ts
```

### Constants, Services & Utilities — kebab-case

```
src/constants/account-types.ts
src/constants/zustand-store-names.ts
src/services/users-api.ts
src/services/query-client.ts
```

### Route files — kebab-case

Expo Router route files in `app/` use **kebab-case** (Expo convention).

```
app/(home)/currency-select.tsx
app/(home)/account-setup.tsx
app/(onboarding)/creating-plan.tsx
```

## Backend (`backend/`)

### Modules — kebab-case

All files inside `src/modules/`, `src/shared/`, `src/middlewares/`, and `src/config/` use kebab-case.

```
src/modules/auth/auth.controller.ts
src/shared/constants.ts
src/middlewares/check-authenticated.ts
```

## Quick Reference

| Directory | Convention | Example |
|-----------|-----------|---------|
| `mobile/src/components/**` | PascalCase | `SearchBar.tsx` |
| `mobile/src/hooks/` | camelCase (`use` prefix) | `useAuthListener.ts` |
| `mobile/src/stores/` | camelCase (`use` prefix) | `useSetupStore.ts` |
| `mobile/src/constants/` | kebab-case | `account-types.ts` |
| `mobile/src/services/` | kebab-case | `users-api.ts` |
| `mobile/app/**` | kebab-case | `account-setup.tsx` |
| `backend/src/**` | kebab-case | `auth.controller.ts` |
